We also started you on an antiarrhythmic ( amiodarone ) to try to convert you into sinus rhythm . After discharge please continue taking your amiodarone . Also please following these instructions : 1. ) Weigh yourself daily ( your current weight is 200 pounds ) . They will then instruct you to change your dose accordingly . Your goal INR is 2 - 3 .
